---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/bridegroom-puts-ring-bride-s-hand-ceremony.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Us"
	description="Learn more about TheEngagementGift and our mission"
	pubDate={new Date('February 01 2026')}
	updatedDate={new Date('March 13 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
	showRelated={false}
>
	<p>
		Welcome to TheEngagementGift! We're a group of seven friends who have all experienced the joy, excitement, and occasional stress of getting engaged. Our shared journey inspired us to create this resource to help others navigate one of life's most meaningful milestones.
	</p>

	<p>
		Each of us has been through the engagement experience—from picking the perfect ring to figuring out what gifts to give or receive. We've learned what works, what doesn't, and most importantly, we've discovered that the best engagement gifts come from thoughtfulness and understanding the couple's unique story.
	</p>

	<p>
		Through this blog, we're sharing our combined experiences, tips, and recommendations to help you find the perfect engagement gifts. Whether you're looking for something luxurious, sentimental, or practical, we've got you covered. Our goal is to make the gift-giving experience as meaningful and stress-free as possible.
	</p>

	<p>
		We believe that celebrating love deserves the same care and attention as the relationship itself. That's why we're committed to providing you with genuine, well-researched gift guides and insights that come from real experience. We hope our blog helps you find that perfect present and celebrate the couples in your life with confidence and joy.
	</p>
</Layout>
